{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/extras/Banner.gif?t=1730290124\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WELCOME TO HUMAN &amp; POWER!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hello, new team member!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are excited to welcome you to our family of professionals dedicated to lighting up the world! As part of your training, we want to introduce you to a unique experience that reflects the challenges and rewards of working with us.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/extras/Arcade.gif?t=1730290124\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THE PROFESSIONALS' ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to dive into a world that combines\u00a0\u0337t\u0337e\u0337r\u0337r\u0337o\u0337r\u0337 roguelike and platformer aspects, constantly challenging expectations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this arcade game, you're not just playing\u2014you\u2019re confronting enemies that threaten our nation! Every run is unique and <i><strong>highly challenging</strong></i>, where you\u2019ll sharpen your skills to become Employee of the Month. With each achievement, you can climb the ranks, competing to see who reaches the top and, perhaps, earning the respect of your peers!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/extras/Corredor.gif?t=1730290124\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PROCEED WITH CAUTION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember: <strong>don\u2019t let curiosity get the best of you</strong>\u2014some mysteries are better left unsolved. What happens in the game may echo beyond, and we know each of you plays a vital role in our mission to power the future!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel the adrenaline, <strong>but don\u2019t face the unknown head-on</strong>. Have fun while learning about the courage and camaraderie that make our team so special. And of course, <i><strong>keep your eyes wide open</strong></i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">. ... -.-. .- .--. . / ..-. .-. --- -- / .-- .... .- - / .--. . .-. ... . -.-. ..- - ... / -.-- --- ..-<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/extras/Monster.gif?t=1730290124\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We look forward to seeing you shine in leadership and lighting our path together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sincerely,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Human&amp;Power</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730290124","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730290124","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/ba4d527e497ed397264d1f7900b169c78e941a5c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730290124","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/ba4d527e497ed397264d1f7900b169c78e941a5c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730290124","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194370/extras/Banner.gif?t=1730290124\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WELCOME TO HUMAN &amp; POWER!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hello, new team member!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are excited to welcome you to our family of professionals dedicated to lighting up the world! As part of your training, we want to introduce you to a unique experience that reflects the challenges and rewards of working with us.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\